		<h1 class="heading-xlarge">Forms</h1>


		<div class="text">

		  <p class="lede">Below you will find a collection of reusable form controls and example forms.</p>

		  <div class="alert-info" role="alert">

				<div class="alert-message">

					<p>When you mark-up elements please ensure that the <b>class tag</b> is used first! This allows for quick visibility for styles associated to elements, and allows for consistency.</p>

				</div>

			</div>

		</div>



